               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18021027-126-cd679" type="crimeDate">22d. of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18021027-126-off678 t18021027-126-cd679"></join>, three watches, valued 8l. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18021027-126-victim1118" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
